            "topic": "QUANTUM MECHANICS — ATOMIC SELECTION RULES",
            "segment": "Why Hydrogen 2s Lives So Long",
            "greeting": "Namaste, Liam",
            "runningText": "checking electric-dipole selection rules and decay channels…",
            "output": [
              "2s to 1s is E1-forbidden.",
              "Two-photon decay provides the slow route."
            ],
